        <abstract> 
<p>Gives consent, which is unnecessary because term of protection has expired, for French translation of <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi>.</p>  
<p>Is at a loss to know how many copies of F. Müller’s <hi rend="italic">Facts and arguments for Darwin</hi> to print.</p>  
<p>The printer is ready for copy for a new "edition" of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>. [Presumably another issue. 2d edition did not appear until 1875.]</p> 
        </abstract>
